high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table then turn right and walk to the fridge in front of you and face it so you can use it.
Open the fridge and grab the tomato that's in front of you then close the fridge door.
Turn around and take a step then turn right to face the sink.
Wash the tomato in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Put the tomato back where you got it then close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: Grab the tomato out of the fridge.
Grab the tomato and head back to the fridge.
Put the tomato back into the fridge
anns.task_desc: Wash the tomato and put it back in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and take the tomato out of the fridge, then close the door.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the sink.
Wash the tomato in the sink and then pick it back up.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk back up to the fridge.
Put the clean tomato in the fridge on the lower shelf, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato in the fridge.
